Package com.grp.application.monitor

The package of monitor.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Monitor
    Class Monitor is the class collects monitor data, maintain monitor state, and set UI elements based on monitor state.
    MonitorState
    Class MonitorState is the class to maintain monitor states based on devices connection and on/off of switches.
    ViewSetter
    Class ViewSetter is the class to set UI elements based on states of monitor.
